    <div class="prose">
	<p>At Midas Touch School of Excellence, we are proud to be guided by a dedicated and passionate leadership team committed to delivering high-quality, holistic education. Our leaders bring a wealth of experience, vision, and integrity to foster a nurturing environment where every child can thrive.</p>
  <h3 class="h2 text-line grow-0">Principal’s Message</h3>
		<p>Our Principal believes in upholding the highest standards of education, focusing on the all-round development of each student. With a strong commitment to academic excellence, critical thinking, and lifelong learning, the Principal ensures that every child’s unique talents and abilities are nurtured and celebrated. Under their guidance, the school continually evolves to meet the dynamic needs of today’s world, promoting innovation in teaching and learning.</p>
       <h3 class="h2 text-line grow-0">Academic Leadership</h3>
	   <p>With the partnership of Next Education India Pvt. Ltd., our academic team integrates modern learning strategies and technologies into the curriculum, ensuring our students receive globally relevant and future-ready education. Our academic leaders are dedicated to continuous improvement, focusing on excellence in academics, extracurricular activities, sports, and personal growth.</p>
       <h3 class="h2 text-line grow-0">Faculty Team</h3>
	   <p>Our highly qualified and experienced teachers are the backbone of the school. They are committed to providing personalized attention and fostering a supportive learning environment. Through dedication and innovative teaching methods, our faculty members empower students to excel both academically and personally.</p>
	   <h3 class="h2 text-line grow-0">Support and Operations Team</h3>
	   <p>Our support staff, including transport managers, food service coordinators, and administrative personnel, play a crucial role in ensuring the smooth and safe operation of the school. Their attention to detail and commitment to student well-being contribute to creating a secure and nurturing school environment.</p>
